came to find him.

43
00:04:09,870 --> 00:04:11,870
No one knows what they talked about.

44
00:04:12,830 --> 00:04:15,390
But Shen Tunan is likely to be entrusted with important duties

45
00:04:15,390 --> 00:04:16,680
by Nanjing.

46
00:04:23,310 --> 00:04:24,070
Hello.

47
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:27,510
Director He?

48
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:28,800
Yes, it’s me.

49
00:04:29,190 --> 00:04:30,480
What can I do for you?

50
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:32,870
Yes.

51
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:36,630
He is doing well,

52
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:40,010
and is pretty capable.

53
00:04:43,870 --> 00:04:44,680
Well,

54
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,480
there's no inconvenience.

55
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:51,090
I'll send him there right away.

56
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:52,360
Don't worry.

57
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:03,390
Mr. Kang.

58
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,320
What happened again?

59
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,450
What's wrong, Mr. Kang?

60
00:05:09,630 --> 00:05:11,190
You've been to Nanjing?

61
00:05:11,190 --> 00:05:12,190
What for?

62
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:15,390
I just received a notice to send you to Jiangxi to fight against the Communist Party.

63
00:05:15,390 --> 00:05:16,120
Really?

64
00:05:16,630 --> 00:05:18,160
You seem very willing to go.

65
00:05:18,310 --> 00:05:20,560
It would be best if I could go.

66
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,390
Jiangxi is the frontline of fighting against the Communists.

67
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:23,390
It's easy to establish merit.

68
00:05:23,390 --> 00:05:25,560
It'll be good for my career too.

69
00:05:28,190 --> 00:05:31,120
The Communist Party has turned Jiangxi upside down.

70
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,240
If you go there now,

71
00:05:34,830 --> 00:05:36,490
are you sure you can come back?

72
00:05:36,950 --> 00:05:37,920
For Kuomintang,

73
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:41,310
I, Qiaosong, am willing to spare no effort until the day I die.

74
00:05:41,310 --> 00:05:42,830
So you already knew

75
00:05:42,830 --> 00:05:44,240
about this arrangement.

76
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:51,380
Wouldn't it be nice to make a fortune with us?

77
00:05:51,390 --> 00:05:53,560
Mr. Kang, let me be honest with you.

78
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:56,360
Even if you were to give me a mountain of gold,

79
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:58,600
it doesn't feel as good as catching a communist

80
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,600
with my own hands.

81
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:04,390
Alright.

82
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,630
Go if you want.

83
00:06:09,750 --> 00:06:11,240
When you arrive in Jiangxi,

84
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:13,240
be sure to make your contributions.

85
00:06:13,270 --> 00:06:14,560
Maybe one day,

86
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:16,620
we'll meet again on the battlefield.

87
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,240
Go on.

88
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:26,200
Mr. Kang, I want to take Wenbiao with me.

89
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:28,630
No.

90
00:06:28,630 --> 00:06:29,750
He's an idiot.

91
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,390
He will cause you trouble.

92
00:06:31,390 --> 00:06:32,270
I'll be watching out for him,

93
00:06:32,270 --> 00:06:33,870
whether or not he is a fool or if he causes trouble.

94
00:06:33,870 --> 00:06:34,830
It's none of your business.

95
00:06:34,830 --> 00:06:35,630
Mr. Kang.

96
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:36,510
Lin Qiaosong.

97
00:06:36,870 --> 00:06:38,240
What do you take me for?

98
00:06:39,750 --> 00:06:40,360
Mr. Kang.

99
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:42,600
I just want to do something for Kuomintang.

100
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:44,630
If you have any instructions for this trip to Jiangxi,

101
00:06:44,630 --> 00:06:46,960
I, Qiaosong, will do my best to cooperate.

102
00:06:53,510 --> 00:06:54,510
Mr. Kang!

103
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,630
Get up.

104
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,090
You two shall go over first,

105
00:07:16,510 --> 00:07:17,510
and scout around.

106
00:07:22,070 --> 00:07:22,830
Get lost.

107
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:24,800
Mr. Kang.

108
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:27,830
Take care.

109
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:57,680
Hello.

110
00:07:58,070 --> 00:07:58,830
Mr. Yu?

111
00:07:59,190 --> 00:08:00,070
Yes, it's me.

112
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:03,830
Something happened to Shen Tunan.

113
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:06,510
I'm worried that

114
00:08:06,870 --> 00:08:08,560
