115
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,080
You two have fun.

116
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:47,640
Lin Qiaosong.

117
00:08:49,870 --> 00:08:50,670
Lin Qiaosong!

118
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,060
What are you doing?

119
00:08:58,720 --> 00:08:59,510
Nothing.

120
00:09:00,870 --> 00:09:02,000
I was just passing by,

121
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,510
and thought I would come see you.

122
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:05,240
I will go back after seeing you.

123
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:08,280
What's wrong?

124
00:09:10,270 --> 00:09:11,530
Did something happen?

125
00:09:13,550 --> 00:09:14,750
Don't think too much.

126
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:16,790
Go back.

127
00:09:20,870 --> 00:09:22,330
Are you leaving Shanghai?

128
00:09:25,270 --> 00:09:26,200
How did you know?

129
00:09:26,790 --> 00:09:27,670
A friend saw you

130
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:31,800
buying a suitcase at Xinshi Department Store.

131
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:34,080
I'm going to Jiangxi to suppress the Communist Party.

132
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,740
I'll leave tomorrow morning.

133
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,940
Buy one more ferry ticket.

134
00:09:43,550 --> 00:09:44,210
I'll go too.

135
00:09:46,630 --> 00:09:47,270
No, you can't.

136
00:09:47,270 --> 00:09:48,080
Cut the crap.

137
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:49,870
If you don't agree,

138
00:09:49,870 --> 00:09:50,840
I'll call Nanjing

139
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:52,050
and report you for selling opium.

140
00:09:52,050 --> 00:09:53,480
I'm going to Jiangxi to suppress the Communists.

141
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:54,960
I'm not going there for a holiday.

142
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:55,910
Going to Jiangxi?

143
00:09:55,910 --> 00:09:57,840
It's more likely than not you will die.

144
00:09:57,840 --> 00:10:00,040
I don't want to not be there when you die.

145
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:19,640
Lin Qiaosong.

146
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:21,840
You dream on.

147
00:10:22,630 --> 00:10:23,600
Even if you die,

148
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:26,220
you can't get rid of me.

149
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:43,100
I owe it to you in my previous life.

150
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:04,670
Hello, comrade.

151
00:11:04,670 --> 00:11:05,120
Hello.

152
00:11:07,510 --> 00:11:08,270
Good morning, comrade.

153
00:11:08,270 --> 00:11:09,080
Morning.

154
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:09,720
Good morning.

155
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:10,520
Good morning.

156
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,250
Hello, comrade.

157
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,410
Comrade Ruolai.

158
00:11:30,510 --> 00:11:31,600
