159
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:32,270
Okay.

160
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:42,550
Sir.

161
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:43,630
Come in.

162
00:11:45,670 --> 00:11:47,400
Chief Lei, you wanted to see me?

163
00:11:48,790 --> 00:11:49,510
Ruolai.

164
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:53,790
Your letter of appointment has been approved.

165
00:11:53,790 --> 00:11:55,920
The president appointed you himself.

166
00:11:57,390 --> 00:11:59,630
You'll be the deputy chief of the General Affairs Unit,

167
00:11:59,630 --> 00:12:00,960
helping me with my work.

168
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,270
Yes.

169
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,480
We'll work together from now on.

170
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:07,150
Okay.

171
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,790
One more thing.

172
00:12:26,630 --> 00:12:27,690
It's unfortunate.

173
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,510
I'm Wei Ruolai, Deputy Chief of the General Affairs Unit,

174
00:12:53,510 --> 00:12:54,870
from the Chinese Soviet Republic National Bank.

175
00:12:54,870 --> 00:12:56,750
Can you call Instructor Shen for me?

176
00:12:56,750 --> 00:12:57,550
Hold on.

177
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,120
Ruolai.

178
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:17,390
Instructor Shen.

179
00:13:17,390 --> 00:13:18,320
You're back.

180
00:13:18,790 --> 00:13:21,320
Yes, I've started work at the bank now.

181
00:13:21,550 --> 00:13:23,320
Have you made up your mind?

182
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:24,150
Yes.

183
00:13:24,870 --> 00:13:26,550
The foundation of finance is credibility.

184
00:13:26,550 --> 00:13:28,670
The Communist Party has great credibility in Jiangxi.

185
00:13:28,670 --> 00:13:29,870
It's very promising.

186
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,390
That's great.

187
00:13:31,390 --> 00:13:32,790
I'm glad that you have the confidence.

188
00:13:32,790 --> 00:13:33,960
I'm happy for you.

189
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:39,920
What's wrong?

190
00:13:40,390 --> 00:13:41,320
Anything else?

191
00:13:43,870 --> 00:13:45,120
Just say it.

192
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:46,270
Don't be a wuss.

193
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:49,910
Chief Lei gave it to me.

194
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:50,870
Take a look.

195
00:14:22,670 --> 00:14:23,390
It's okay.

196
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:24,870
I've got it.

197
00:14:26,630 --> 00:14:27,360
Thank you.

198
00:15:02,630 --> 00:15:03,890
You're the only sister

199
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:06,750
I have in this world.

200
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:08,750
I choose to believe you,

201
00:15:10,270 --> 00:15:11,800
and I want to believe in you.

202
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:16,490
Thank you, Brother.

203
00:15:42,150 --> 00:15:42,910
Brother.

204
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:51,600
Brother.

205
00:15:53,150 --> 00:15:54,480
No matter where you are,

206
00:15:56,510 --> 00:15:58,120
I'll always be your sister.

207
00:17:08,069 --> 00:17:08,640
Ruolai,

208
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:10,960
do you want to take me as your mentor?

209
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:12,290
I was born by my parents,

210
00:17:12,829 --> 00:17:14,359
but I am taught by my mentor.

211
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:15,750
Mentor Shen,

212
00:17:16,160 --> 00:17:18,310
please accept three bows from me, Ruolai.

213
00:17:18,310 --> 00:17:19,970
I will do my best in the future,

214
00:17:20,200 --> 00:17:21,660
and I will not let you down.

215
00:18:54,790 --> 00:18:55,850
We've reached, Yu.

216
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:03,790
Nanchang Field Headquarters' Suppression Army.

217
00:19:03,790 --> 00:19:05,350
Special Commissioner Tu, welcome to Ganzhou.

218
00:19:05,350 --> 00:19:06,000
Hello.

219
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:07,660
Take their suitcases.

220
00:19:07,750 --> 00:19:08,400
Mom.

221
00:19:08,830 --> 00:19:11,590
Dad, how long are we going to stay in Ganzhou?

222
00:19:11,880 --> 00:19:14,590
Ganzhou has a lot of mountains and a great view.

223
00:19:15,070 --> 00:19:17,130
We could be here for a long time, okay?

224
00:19:27,550 --> 00:19:29,350
Master, Madam, Miss, hello.

225
00:19:29,480 --> 00:19:30,790
Dazhuang, Erzhuang, take their suitcases.

226
00:19:30,790 --> 00:19:32,640
Xiaoju, Xiaofeng, go make tea.

227
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:33,880
We're here.

228
00:19:36,070 --> 00:19:37,070
Slow down.

229
00:19:39,310 --> 00:19:41,370
There are so many lotus flowers here.

230
00:19:44,590 --> 00:19:45,750
Slow down, Miss.

231
00:19:49,350 --> 00:19:50,400
Slow down, Yu.

232
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:51,750
Miss, slow down.

233
00:19:55,110 --> 00:19:56,200
It's so big.

234
00:19:57,350 --> 00:19:59,200
This place is nothing compared to Shanghai.

235
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:00,590
I'm sorry to make you go through this.

236
00:20:00,590 --> 00:20:02,270
No, I think this place is nice.

237
00:20:02,790 --> 00:20:05,790
It looks like the house I lived in when I was a kid.

238
00:20:06,240 --> 00:20:07,070
Really?

239
00:20:07,070 --> 00:20:07,920
Mom.

240
00:20:07,920 --> 00:20:09,480
Mom, come and take a look!

241
00:20:09,480 --> 00:20:10,230
Coming.

242
00:20:15,510 --> 00:20:16,160
Sir.

243
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:18,680
Sir.

244
00:20:19,310 --> 00:20:20,000
Sir.

245
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:20,800
What's wrong?

246
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:22,520
I overheard them saying in the car that

247
00:20:22,520 --> 00:20:24,510
Lin Qiaosong is coming to Jiangxi too.

248
00:20:24,510 --> 00:20:25,680
He seems to have been parachuted in.

249
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:27,080
He'll be here in two days.

250
00:20:28,550 --> 00:20:31,080
It seems that Nanjing still doesn't trust me.

251
00:20:31,270 --> 00:20:33,160
They sent someone with a grudge to keep an eye on me.

252
00:20:33,160 --> 00:20:34,420
What should we do, Sir?

253
00:20:35,160 --> 00:20:36,690
The armed forces in Ganzhou

254
00:20:37,110 --> 00:20:38,240
is under the control of

255
00:20:38,240 --> 00:20:40,110
the Brigade Commander of Guangdong Army, Qian Fengshi.

256
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:43,000
Chen Jitang of the Guangdong Army does not listen to the chairman of the Standing Committee.

257
00:20:43,000 --> 00:20:45,240
Therefore, Qian Fengshi will also not listen to me.

258
00:20:45,240 --> 00:20:46,900
Now that Lin Qiaosong is here,

259
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:48,110
it's not that we can't work together,

260
00:20:48,110 --> 00:20:51,040
but that we will just use each other for our own needs.

261
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:53,040
A bustling, cosmopolitan city,

262
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:54,880
a place of fireworks,

263
00:20:55,110 --> 00:20:56,750
where the elites gather.

264
00:20:57,640 --> 00:20:58,700
The Shanghai Bund.

265
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:06,270
Brother,

266
00:21:06,830 --> 00:21:08,790
why do we have to go to Jiangxi?

267
00:21:09,400 --> 00:21:10,480
We have to go even if we don't want to.

268
00:21:10,480 --> 00:21:11,940
I can go anywhere with you.

269
00:21:12,550 --> 00:21:13,240
Really?

270
00:21:14,920 --> 00:21:15,640
Well,

271
00:21:16,030 --> 00:21:17,830
I still don't quite understand.

272
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:19,880
We were doing fine in Shanghai.

273
00:21:19,880 --> 00:21:20,960
We had status,

274
00:21:20,960 --> 00:21:22,560
and we were making big money.

275
00:21:22,590 --> 00:21:24,270
Why do you have to go to Jiangxi,

276
00:21:24,270 --> 00:21:26,750
and put your life on the line to fight the Communists?

277
00:21:26,750 --> 00:21:28,880
I was right when I said you were a moron.

278
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:31,750
How long do you think we can sell opium for?

279
00:21:31,750 --> 00:21:33,720
If something happens, they will be protected.

280
00:21:33,720 --> 00:21:34,640
But for us,

281
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:35,680
we will die.

282
00:21:38,300 --> 00:21:40,400
Let's just talk about the recent construction treasury bill.

283
00:21:40,400 --> 00:21:42,730
Those from the banks who were close to them

284
00:21:43,070 --> 00:21:45,930
were also ripped off and lost their family fortune.

285
00:21:46,510 --> 00:21:48,570
Some even lost their family members.

286
00:21:50,110 --> 00:21:50,790
